===Pronunciation===
χαίρω / chairō / khah'ee-ro
===Etymology===

A primary verb; 
===Verb===
'''χαίρω'''

#to be full of “cheer”, that is, calmly happy or well off; impersonal especially as a salutation (on meeting or parting), be well: - farewell, be glad, God speed, greeting, [[hail]], joy (-fully), [[rejoice]].